name: Zunozap
body:
ZunoZap (zoo-u-no-z-ah-p) is A simple web browser coded in Java ZunoZap is in HIGHY DEVELMENT! Do not use as your main browser yet!

## Downloads: The one on top is the newest! [ZunoZap-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-04.jar](https://github.com/ZunoZap/zunozap/raw/master/builds/ZunoZap-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-04.jar) [ZunoZap-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-03.jar](https://github.com/ZunoZap/zunozap/raw/master/builds/ZunoZap-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-03.jar) [ZunoZap-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-02.jar](https://github.com/ZunoZap/zunozap/raw/master/builds/ZunoZap-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-02.jar)
